<div class="ma3 ma4-m ma4-l">
  <p class="b">
    Are you sure you want to disconnect your account from SLaM?
  </p>
  <p>
    If you disconnect, you will no longer be able to send / receive messages
    with your SLaM Care team or see Care Plan updates in Healthlocker. Your
    Care team will no longer be able to view your tracking graphs or any new
    Goals and Coping Strategies you create.
  </p>

  <p>You can connect again in the future if you wish.</p>

  <div class="flex mw6 center justify-between">
    <div class="mt4">
      <%= link_secondary "Yes, disconnect", to: account_path(@conn, :disconnect),
      method: "put" %>
    </div>

    <div class="mt4">
      <%= link_primary "No, take me back", to: account_path(@conn, :index) %>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>
